Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}DECEMBER 20
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}MIDDLE\NJUMP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently at Mid Jump, sexual content is okay\Nif it doesn't go on for more than four pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? That sounds obscene.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right. It is obscene.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The cover for that magazine\Nis obscene, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Agreed. It is obscene, isn't it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.37,0:00:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}CHRISTMAS CAKE\NACCEPTING ORDERS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While we've been focused\Non the culture festival,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the rest of the world\Nhas gone into Christmas-mode.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}NO OCCUPANCY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All these couples using Christmas Eve\Nas a pretext for hooking up...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No vacancies\Nat any of the love hotels.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}NO OCCUPANCY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the day,\Nour world revolves around sex!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Awful! Awful! So obscene!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They all have nothing\Nbut indecent thoughts on their minds!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then... And then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Indecent thoughts, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was that kiss, then?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There were...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,all these tiny balloons everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}SQUEAL SQUEAL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was gorgeous beyond belief!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And then, President told me\Nto apply to Stanford!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That is, he ordered me\Nto join him in the U.S.!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.07,0:01:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stanford?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know! What was he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But the way he said it with that blush\Non his face was just so adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I said yes in spite of myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And in spite of myself, I kissed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know, Hayasaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.39,0:01:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}When you kiss someone you like,\Nit can't be a regular kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.72,0:01:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}LADY KAGUYA'S\NKEY TIPS FOR KISSING
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Class is now in session!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You place your lips together like so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The grown-up way is to slip your tongue in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kashiwagi and her boyfriend actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}WAR CRIMINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, you didn't know that,\Ndid you, Hayasaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Idi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}DECEMBER 21
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the culture festival over,\Nthe student council goes back to normal life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the scars still\Nrun deep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ishigami's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Shirogane's battle\Nis far from over!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I let her know how I feel!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I even kissed her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it was a pretty intense one!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meaning...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we can be considered\Nboyfriend and girlfriend now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}But how pure was that kiss, really?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I'd mismanaged\Nthe distance between us here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:04:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's this, President? One kiss,\Nand you're acting like my boyfriend?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That kiss only happened\Nbecause we were having a moment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Surely you don't think\Nthat a kiss makes us lovers now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's exactly how a cherry boy's mind would work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}CHERRY BOY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How cute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}GAH
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,President, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today, I'm going to set things straight\Nwith Shinomiya!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here she comes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}DAINTY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}TROT TROT
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shinomiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't she seem different today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh... Oh... Oh... Oh... Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,she does look\Nmore childish than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Little Kaguya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Little Kaguya?\N- Little Kaguya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Little Kaguya! Little Kaguya! Little Kaguya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think we'd get to see you this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! How lucky are we\Nto get to see Little Kaguya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck\Ndo you mean by "Little Kaguya"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaguya's personality undergoes slight shifts\Ndepending on her mental state that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're all aware of that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Little Kaguya can only show up if she meets\Nthe most stringent conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,60% happy, 40% in denial and, on top\Nof that, she has to be sleep-deprived.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}IN DENIAL
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every single one of these boxes\Nneeds to be checked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}LITTLE KAGUYA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And only when her psychological balance hits\Nthat sweet spot does this rare Little Kaguya appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Rare Kaguya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Even I've still only seen her three times!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}How is this even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}That's right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}DECEMBER 20
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The conditions had already been met\Nthe previous night!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A grown-up kiss!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In a nutshell,\Na dizzying array of kisses exist.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A kiss on the cheek or hand\Nsignifying affection.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A kiss on the lips\Nindicating a close relationship.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the more meaningful kind of kiss.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}LOVE BIBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this the way\None normally kisses the one she loves?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}KISSES THAT WORK\NFOR ROMANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It says so in the books I've read.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even Miss Kashiwagi and her boyfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kashiwagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kashiwagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how one typically\Ngoes about kissing another?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Um... Um—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was a special kind of kiss\Nyou only give to the person you love!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So whatever you do,\Ndon't kiss anyone else like that, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}War criminal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Such disinformation was pumped\Ninto Kaguya, a stranger to girl talk...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The kind of kiss you only give\Nto the one you love...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}To the one you love!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And she ends up doing just that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was your first-ever kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't in a love scene\Nin a Hollywood movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's a regular kiss, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not by a long shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be kissing like that\Non school grounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's something\Nyou should be doing in bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That kind of kiss...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}practically amounts to having sex!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:06:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Se...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...x?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She managed to say it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "sex"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was insert my tongue\Ninto his oral cavity!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That can't possibly be sex!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's something you do\Nin the process of having sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop repeating the word "sex"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've been repeating it\Nyourself, Lady Kaguya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Christmas is around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since you've gotten this far already,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it will be a breeze to take it\Nto the next level and have sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Why on earth would you go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't people normally wait at least a month or two\Nafter their first kiss to engage in that sort of thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}HOLLER HOLLER
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}HOLLER HOLLER
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}HOLLER HOLLER
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a different story if you've already\Ngone that far with your first kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}HOLLER HOLLER
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I'm just not getting through to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}This is why children like you\Nwho've never been kissed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're thinking of something\Nunbelievably infuriating right now, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting nowhere with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask someone with experience\Nabout what to actually expect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}MISS KASHIWAGI\NNOW DIALING
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Kaguya? What a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd like to ask you something,\NMiss Kashiwagi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Ask me anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, you see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About how long did you wait\Nto have sex after your first kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll have you know, Tsubasa and I\Nhave never done anything so indec—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't ridicule me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't be more serious than I am now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a serious conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After that first kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,maybe two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! You'd wait\Nat least that long, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, how long after a grown-up kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About 40 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you finally starting\Nto see the light, Lady Kaguya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just acknowledge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That because your first kiss was a deep dive,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chances are that President sees you\Nas a super-nympho lust monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A super-nympho lust monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can I possibly look him\Nin the eye tomorrow?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In an abrupt about-face\Nafter that Ultra Romantic night,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}THAT CAN'T POSSIBLY BE SEX!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}A SUPER-NYMPHO\NLUST MONSTER!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the point that Hayasaka brought up\Nhas caused her to spend a night of agony!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}MNGH\NNNGH
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And sleep-deprivation ensues!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaguya's brain plunges even further\Ninto the depths of malfunction!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Resulting in two straight days of zero IQ!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Intellectually, it's Black Monday!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}And...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Rare Kaguya?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Descent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a hundred times better\Nthan her being scary, so I accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaaaat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn! Today of all days,\NI really wanted to talk to Shinomiya!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In this state,\NI can't even get through to her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}GRIND\NGRIND
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is bad!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wh-Wh-What is it, Shinomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Pwesident, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Actually, maybe it's perfect.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Who is this adorable creature?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Needless to say,\Nshe's in a super-deformed state.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is how she appears to everyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, how old are you, Little Kaguya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Um... Seventeen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seventeen, huh? What a sweetheart!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}CONGRATULATIONS\NON COMING OF AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Did you know? If you're 17,\Nthen next year, you'll be an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's not a good look to take advantage of someone\Nwhen they're vulnerable, Ishigami. So cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So cuddly and fluffy!\NI want to display you at my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}SQUISH\NSQUISH
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}WHACK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}SQUISH\NSQUISH
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey! You can't hit people, you bad girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We just caught a glimpse\Nof Shinomiya's inner psyche, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see she doesn't like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}SQUIRM\NSQUIRM
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just let her go, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's totally fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Little Kaguya loves me the best, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, show us\Nwho your favorites are in order!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:10:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:10:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Number two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:10:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Number three.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me, but I think\Nshe just went with the flow there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}MINI DONUTS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're giving me a snack?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}SMITTEN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're giving me one, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}RATTLE...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sniff!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll run out and get some candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're going at top speed,\Nso hang on, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Shinomiya, about yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Pwesident...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We're the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's no good. We can't talk like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, it seems like Shinomiya's brain\Nis the size of an orange.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's probably seeing a different world than I am.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come to think of it, I've heard\Nthat if the gap between your IQ is 20 or so,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:12:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there's no way\Nyou can hold a conversation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}In that case...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chinomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pwesident?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chinomiya, let's talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should we talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anything you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chinomiya! Chinomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pwesident! Pwesident!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chinomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pwesident! Pwesident! Pwesident!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}They're holding a conversation,\Nand it's scarily devoid of substance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm late—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chinomiya! Chinomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pwesident! Pwesident!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chinomiya! Chinomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pwesident! Pwesident!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chinomiya! Chinomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pwesident! Pwesident!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chinomiya! Chinomiya! Chinomiya! Chinomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pwesident! Pwesident! Pwesident! Pwesident!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aren't you both too old\Nto be doing whatever this is?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Super-deformed is just super-deformed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:13:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}DECEMBER 20
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Three days until Christmas Eve!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Having shared a grown-up kiss,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:13:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these two are about to see the curtain go up\Non this year's final romantic battle of minds!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For Hayasaka, it was the morning from hell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Little Kaguya's fast asleep, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm not surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}MNGH\NNNGH
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The culture festival must've worn her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let's let her get some real rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}BAKED\NSENBEI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}MIDDLE\NJUMP
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, almost forgot.\NI brought this week's Mid Jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}TWO PUNCH MAN
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}MS. KUBO\NDOESN'T MAKE IT\NCOMPLICATED
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's lewd material you have there.\NI'm confiscating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you come from, Iino?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Iino...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,can you at least wait\Nuntil President finishes it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Negative! The rules are the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You only have yourself to blame\Nfor bringing in contraband!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same old, same old, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Makes you wonder if it's going to be\Nlike this until we graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We're going to be\Nat each other's throats until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but whenever you do something to me,\NI can't rest until I get back at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you promise never to bring\Nanything like this again,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you have your book back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep your word on that,\Nand the odds of us getting along might be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,more than...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not going to happen.\NI'm so going to bring another one next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How do you not see\Nthat it's your own fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}PUNCH\NMISS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Are you stupid? Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An old-school brawl?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ouch! I'll bring it, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ts-Tsubame!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind us, please.\NWe're always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}After I made such a huge concession...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! There's something\NI wanted to ask you, Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you'll be free\Non Christmas Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this? No way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, if you don't feel like it,\Nyou can totally say no, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna come over that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}YAY
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoa, Tsubame's house? On Christmas?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In Tsubame's room?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's beyond perverted!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It's not like that!\NI was planning to invite you, too, Iino!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For a threesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'll be inviting a lot of people!\NI'm going to throw a party!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's an orgy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you clueless\NDisciplinary Committee member!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How do you not get that she's talking\Nabout a Christmas party?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-O-Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry. That just never crossed\Nmy mind when I said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, if Iino wasn't around,\NI totally would've gotten the wrong idea, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm inviting the Cheerleading Squad\Nand the Culture Festival Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei says she'll be coming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubame!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm in the middle\Nof an errand here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so let me know if you're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}STUDENT COUNCIL ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ishigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you free on Christmas Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna come over that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you having a Christmas party?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you made the connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's have a Christmas party for everyone in the\Nstudent council! I'll provide my home as the venue!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll come, too, won't you, Kaguya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:15:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}MNGH\NNNGH
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she just moaning in her sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You won't have to spend another lonely Eve\Nall by yourself this year, Ishigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Chika,\Nyour brilliant event planner—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, sorry, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but on Christmas Eve,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of a shame that your howls of laughter\Nwill go to waste, but it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It really is true.\NTsubame just invited Ishigami and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You can't possibly turn down an invitation\Nfrom Tsubame, can you, Ishigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A BIT DISAPPOINTED
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Huh? Why couldn't I, if it's her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Everyone here is aware\Nthat you have a crush on Tsubame.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe around the sports festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which party are you going to, Iino?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I know you think\NI'd be a thorn in your side. So I guess I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I don't think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is... that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}GOOD NIGHT!!\NSEE YOU LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}IINO AND I WILL BOTH\NATTEND YOUR\NCHRISTMAS PARTY\NLOOKING FORWARD TO IT
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to give him my answer\Nthree months from now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}LOST AND FOUND
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}IF NO ONE'S CLAIMED IT\NIN THREE MONTHS, TAKE IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If no one's claimed it\Nin three months, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I really want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Christmas, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I wonder what Shinomiya's going to do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The second battle of minds\Ninside her own brain and the trial begin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:18:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TWO GENIUSES' WAR OF LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}WHAT? I'M UP!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did the defendant steal a kiss\Nfrom Miyuki Shirogane without warning,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}THE ACCUSED KAGUYA (STUPID)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but she even inserted her tongue,\Nof all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She is therefore charged with the crime proscribed\Nin article 174 of our personal penal code...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Grown-Up Kiss Offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, the defendant is deemed\Na flight risk who may flee the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, the prosecution seeks\Nthe death penalty for the defendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}THE COMPLETE\NSIX CODES\NOF JAPAN
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}PROSECUTOR KAGUYA\N(COLD AS ICE)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Death penalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}COUNSEL KAGUYA SHINOMIYA
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No objections.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My own lawyer won't even defend me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Pwesident is in the student council room...\NWow, it's perfect!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uttering gibberish\Nin front of President...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Number one...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}NUMBER ONE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Saying he was your number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.68,0:18:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what a convenient mind you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why is it such a big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,President used all those balloons\Nto let me know how he feels!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, you do have a point, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How ludicrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you letting\Nmere balloons rattle you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}AHHH
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not looking like yourself, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:19:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My internal breakers broke, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Playtime is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've been summoned today so that\Nwe can decide what to do going forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a crucial decision\Nthat will determine our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}PRESIDING JUDGE KAGUYA\N(CHILD)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are three issues under discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}(1) ON OUR RELATIONSHIP WITH PRESIDENT\N(2) ON STUDYING ABROAD\N(3) ON THAT GROWN-UP KISS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let us resolve them one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,our relationship with President.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we've got to be lovers now!\NI mean, we've kissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right, we are, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}SMOOCH
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If kissing makes you lovers,\Nthen sex workers would be lovers with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Although our feelings are undeniably mutual,\Nwe've never been vocal about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we're to take it to the next level,\Nwe should say so directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then regarding Number 1,\Nour conclusion must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(1) ON OUR RELATIONSHIP\NWITH MIYUKI SHIROGANE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}A.\NMORE THAN\NFRIENDS\NLESS THAN\NLOVERS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next, let's discuss studying abroad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}(2) ON STUDYING ABROAD
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, President did say\Nit was a once-in-a-lifetime wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so going!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Huuuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seriously believe\Nyou'll be allowed to do such a thing, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How do you plan to talk Father into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Consider it a blessing that you've been able\Nto distance yourself from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must refrain at all costs from doing anything\Nthat would awaken the sleeping tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I already told him I'd go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.57,0:20:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keeping your promises, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You need something in your life\Nthat you can have absolute faith in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the policy you live by?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.41,0:20:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when you fail, it might be\Nthe last time I ever see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(2) ON STUDYING ABROAD
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}A.\NGO WITH\NPRESIDENT
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, regarding that grown-up kiss...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what are we going to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Seriously, what are we going to do? Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,President might be thinking\Nthat I'm a super-nympho lust monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean it, what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All you have to do is explain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That you just misread the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:20:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that would be embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think it would be better\Nto take the stance of a grown-up woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}A KISS?\NTHAT'S NO MORE\NTHAN A GREETING
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a ludicrous conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you never should've kissed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, a kiss is something\Nthat the man should seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A woman going for a kiss...\NHow disgraceful is that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're being sexist!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's right! Who decided\Nthat a woman can't kiss first?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have no clue, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather have a kiss stolen from me,\Nnot the other way around!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What? But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Because it would make my heart\Npound harder that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.85,0:21:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We all have different fetishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kissing impulsively...\NWe're not beasts in the wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}IRRITATED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would it kill you to learn a little restraint?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural to want\Nto kiss someone you're in love with!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! If you really love someone,\Nthere's just no holding back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can say stuff like that\Nbecause you're not in love with President, Ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,not in love with...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki Shirogane?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You happy-go-lucky insurgents...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.25,0:22:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see the forest for the trees\Nbecause you put your own feelings first!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.43,0:22:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have no idea how much I've held back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.60,0:22:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How I've continued to hold back all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was none other than I\Nwho first fell in love with Miyuki Shirogane!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,More than you two ever have!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.65,0:22:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also the one who's the most serious\Nabout my future with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.57,0:22:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here I am, racking my brain\Nto find a way to make him mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,yet you both keep doing as you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How arrogant of you,\Nyou Kaguya-come-latelys!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.28,0:22:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.62,0:22:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't argue with yourself. It's just sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.16,0:22:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right! In the first place, it doesn't matter\Nwho fell in love with him first!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, aren't you even happy\Nthat President kissed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, would you shut up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.67,0:22:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like your brains\Nare in la-la land, you morons!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.64,0:22:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare lecture me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been longing all this time\Nfor President to kiss me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, what were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go die and rot in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.44,0:23:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For once in your lives,\Nconsider my feelings, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.57,0:23:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you sure\Nyou want to conceal the real you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.34,0:23:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake, Shinomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.44,0:23:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.90,0:23:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I've been fast asleep for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.81,0:23:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.23,0:23:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Shirogane.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.24,0:23:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd appreciate a cup of coffee, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.99,0:24:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}I'm throwing\Na Christmas party at\Nmy place this year.\NWanna come?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.99,0:24:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, I'll come\Nif I can make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.99,0:24:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Sis texted me\Nthat Kaguya will be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.00,0:24:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}I'M COMING
